description: Gerry O'Connel has only a short time to complete his fashion catalog or he will be fired. He frantically calls the 3 people needed to get the job done: the model agent, Taylor Hill, the cameraman, Carson Michaels and the make-up artist, Pietro White. As fate would have it, these 3 are embroiled in a torrid 3-way together, with each phone call only momentarily interrupting their unbridled passion. Both Taylor and Pietro fuck the, oh so willing, ass of humpy Carson, his moans echoing through the bedroom. Pietro nuts right into the mouth of Taylor as he speaks on the phone with Gerry and Carson's load is volcanic as he coats his own chest and both partners hungrily lick him clean.
title: DJK Productions: Catalog Shooters, Scene #01
